  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"501968265\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.42592592592592593\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" width=\"1800\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=85440bbf&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fg0kpxARkI2T5VyXpKDCIicI7kJvSvyX52fmricOTWgpzGdPq7Ficcwq6fwZCG6NEj3TKsTOmLLA18PcTvoI3nwYsg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <blockquote style=\"padding:16px 20px;color:rgb(80, 80, 80);visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:18px;border-color:initial;line-height:1.64;box-sizing:border-box !important;quotes:none;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;border-radius:4px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;margin-top:20px;border-width:initial;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:20px;border-style:none;\">\n   <p style=\"max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;visibility: visible;text-align: left;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">「有意思小周刊」是我利用零碎时间，梳理记录一周的日常阅读与思考内容。目的是为以后更好构建自己知识体系，也为了将这些内容分享给你。</span></span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <h3 style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;white-space: normal;line-height: 2em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(1, 194, 96);\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">以下是这期值得关注的内容</span></strong></span></h3>\n  <h3 style=\"margin: 24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: left;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">📰 推荐阅读</span></span></h3>\n  <ne-clipboard source=\"https%3A%2F%2Fwww.yuque.com%2Fqone%2Fyys%2Fov5db57v4bsast73%23BGkxc\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"></ne-clipboard>\n  <ol style=\"line-height: 1.6em;text-indent: 0em;font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;\">我开源的 DeepSeek 模板，被免费复制4.8万次，还上了扣子Coze首页推荐！</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;\">让AI编程的价值可追踪、可量化--「AI编程效能量化系统」</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;\">得物管理类目配置线上化：从业务痛点到技术实现</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;\">设计即对话, 技术与美的交融</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;\">从代码到配置：如何用SQL配置实现数据核对</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;\">一次AI驱动的淘宝客户端需求开发实战</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;\">李沐：年度演讲谈智能体！</span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ol>\n  <h4 style=\"margin: 24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: left;line-height: 1.6em;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">🎯 言论·语录</span></span></strong></h4>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-indent: 0em;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: left;line-height: 1.6em;\"><ne-clipboard data=\"%7B%22type%22%3A%22fragment%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22%23fragment%22%2C%22children%22%3A%5B%7B%22type%22%3A%22element%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22uad39aad0%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22oli%22%2C%22attrs%22%3A%7B%22list%22%3A%22u1f9aab83%22%2C%22indexType%22%3A0%2C%22indexStyle%22%3A%7B%7D%2C%22fid%22%3A%22ua8b54bf8%22%2C%22parentIndex%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22index%22%3A0%7D%2C%22children%22%3A%5B