578px;text-wrap: wrap;\">做一些没有意义的事，找到你的活人感</span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ol>\n  <p data-track=\"34\" style=\"visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:18px;border-color:initial;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;outline:0px;max-width:100%;margin-top:20px;border-width:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0em;border-style:initial;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-cropsely2=\"65\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.11296296296296296\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:578px;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:center;height:65px;\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=be35e013&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fg0kpxARkI2QPgPA868wyn0LFMFlv18uosEWwB4iaKPdBBHJlD4GYRHOytPia6moa4MPQDibjKXtvUvts27RcWa5OQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></span></p>\n  <ne-clipboard source=\"https%3A%2F%2Fwww.yuque.com%2Fqone%2Fyys%2Fov5db57v4bsast73%23BGkxc\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"></ne-clipboard>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 8px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px;\">▌我开源的 DeepSeek 模板，被免费复制4.8万次，还上了扣子Coze首页推荐！</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg2MTYzNzM5OA==&amp;mid=2247518121&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=2ddbf111a3549afec3eca4f1460eec28&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"></a><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/8FuA2z1KVKTIPh0d1Z4oxA\" target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/8FuA2z1KVKTIPh0d1Z4oxA</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">本文介绍了作者开源的 DeepSeek 模板在扣子（Coze）平台上的能力增强版的实现、实际应用与扩展方向。内容要点包括：通过一键免费复制与多插件生态，提升模型能力（含联网搜索、图片理解、文档生成等），比较推理模型与通用模型的差异以选取合适场景，以及通过海量插件、专属知识库和专家角色设定等维度实现能力扩展，最终给出可重复的搭建步骤、实际运行对比与扩展前景。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"501968267\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5407407407407407\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1080\" width=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=53b83f7c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Fg0kpxARkI2T5VyXpKDCIicI7kJvSvyX52zoLFlpicA9AosAzc43o2Fw8BdCphwGw4C2tFVuU8ae26JByzapiaEO3w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 8px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px;\">▌让AI编程的价值可追踪、可量化--「AI编程效能量化系统」</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI0MjczMjM2NA==&amp;mid=2247499036&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=293ae1d7d10f361133995137f7c82a6f&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"></a><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/A8TqyFNcSnbM11_3xSR24A\" target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/A8TqyFNcSnbM11_3xSR24A</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">本文介绍了一套名为“AI编程效能量化系统”的方案，旨在解决AI编程中对话难以追踪与贡献难以量化的痛点，通过在本地插件与云端分析相结合的方式，实现对AI对话、生成代码与实际产出之间关系的可追溯和可量化，并以核心指标和仪表盘形式展示个人与团队的AI贡献与产能提升。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"501968266\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5074074074074074\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1080\" width=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=241364d6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Fg0kpxARkI2T5VyXpKDCIicI7kJvSvyX523weFP9nPJc5hOteAQbiaJhHiamOgMJDRWJOsV968W8hiaLEJe0NjpDbyw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 8px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px;\">▌得物管理类目配置线上化：从业务痛点到技术实现</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkxNTE3ODU0NA==&amp;mid=2247541530&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=a00c3e72e03feb1938d29cae6b4a21bb&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"></a><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/XRkYpewqgu76c4IOYNEquw\" target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/XRkYpewqgu76c4IOYNEquw</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">本文围绕“管理类目配置线上化”展开，聚焦通过分层架构、核心模块、数据模型、数仓计算等全链路技术手段，解决管理类目规则高频迭代、校验复杂、以及对下游系统的耦合等痛点，将规则迭代上线周期从数周缩短至1-2天，同时通过规则生命周期管理、状态机驱动和飞书通知等机制，提升效率、降低风险，并实现规则模型化与自动化校验的长期技术积累。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"501968268\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.9898734177215189\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"790\" width=\"790\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=190c4cd7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Fg0kpxARkI2T5VyXpKDCIicI7kJvSvyX522cMHp929nMRpbas2atfiaQjnXop7am8pBb8hJR6nKGbtme5giciaz3QLQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 8px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;t