x;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px;\">▌从代码到配置：如何用SQL配置实现数据核对</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI0MjIxNjE0OQ==&amp;mid=2247506649&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=054d12998256dfd5a5f2b0ce273dc0f1&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"></a><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/jlO-Phozp9KqfxvR5GjsfA\" target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/jlO-Phozp9KqfxvR5GjsfA</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">本文通过将数据核对规则从代码硬编码转向配置化的 SQL 实现，阐明了“数据查询 + 条件判断”的本质，展示了 SQL 配置化在核对场景中的高效、低成本、可控性优势，以及基于内存快照、血缘分析和数据指纹分组等核心技术实现，最终实现规则上线从天级缩短至分钟级，并具备在线调试、跨库执行与高并发协作能力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"501968269\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6203703703703703\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1080\" width=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7547a1bb&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Fg0kpxARkI2T5VyXpKDCIicI7kJvSvyX52aJXyicic3SSL7Gs0zQ3rxPSQDOfhhicmiaRR8DwJlaNwynroZR5U0EWxTA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg