52SjJrtqRsOL2iaic2wu0N58Fs4qYIOkZJlMZPnbZ7kVjbptXwWwPciaiaRw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 8px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px;\">▌李沐：年度演讲谈智能体！</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIyNjM2MzQyNg==&amp;mid=2247714346&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=a003e0f7a1f619f179052de43dfe4b01&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"></a><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/7g7ZEGKVlT2OLfSGRMKzhA\" target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/7g7ZEGKVlT2OLfSGRMKzhA</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">沐神在硅谷101举办的年度科技大会中，进行了一段关于语音智能体（Voice Agent）落地应用的精彩分享。他通过回顾两个实际项目——如何在开放世界游戏中，让智能体同时扮演“游戏设计师+游戏NPC”的双重角色，为玩家带来独一无二的体验；又如何通过严苛的行业认证，让AI成为能卖出保险的智能电话销售员——深入剖析了语音智能体从技术挑战到商业落地的关键经验和最佳实践。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"501968271\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5222222222222223\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1080\" width=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=08cefd91&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Fg0kpxARkI2T5VyXpKDCIicI7kJvSvyX5233KULZzjiah3cubRU5bF2HbxEvaHPT1usS2GqRIBqibibH1CAGZAf7ynA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <div style=\"margin: 24px 8px 8px;white-space: normal;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;\">\n   <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:48px 8px 0em;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;clear:both;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-cropsely2=\"65\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.11296296296296296\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;vertical-align: bottom;height: 65px;width: 578px;\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d8a4b282&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fg0kpxARkI2QPgPA868wyn0LFMFlv18uoQrLTibmRJELUQysO80354ouUOACwWDCCr0NXNjicZbicDGqrqvPSHdibicQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></span></p>\n   <h2 data-node-type=\"block\" data-block-type=\"text\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;text-align:justify;\"><ne-clipboard source=\"https%3A%2F%2Fwww.yuque.com%2Fqone%2Fyys%2Fov5db57v4bsast73%23BGkxc\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"></ne-clipboard></h2>\n   <h2 style=\"margin: 24px 8px 8px;white-space: normal;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px;\">▌做一些没有意义的事，找到你的活人感</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA4OTgxNzM3OQ==&amp;mid=2652582389&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=90385ff0f6e17cd8574a7c2a1c991609&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"></a><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/7Bu8cyIIX3VuFliZwBpFvA\" target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/7Bu8cyIIX3VuFliZwBpFvA</a></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;min-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">本文主张在追求个人商业成功时，需适度从“效率优先”的单一导向中解放出来，通过做“没有直接意义”的事情来保持活力、好奇心和表达力，从而建立更稳健的个人能力与可持续的商业模式；同时强调自由与自我认同的重要性，抗拒模板化和单纯AI驱动的内容生产，强调“活人感”的稀缺性，以及在尝试多元路径中逐步形成有用的商业价值。</span></span></p>\n   <div data-role=\"outer\" label=\"edit by 135editor\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n    <div data-tools=\"hack\" data-id=\"hack\">\n     <div data-support=\"96编辑器\" data-style-id=\"31634\">\n      <div style=\"text-align: center;margin: 48px 0px 10px;\">\n       <div style=\"display: flex;justify-content: center;align-items: center;\">\n        <div style=\"width:20%;color:#77af51;font-size:20px;margin-bottom:12px;\" data-width=\"20%\">\n         <div style=\"margin:0px 10px;\">\n          <p><strong><span leaf=\"\">END</span></strong></p>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
